{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Noun===
'''antelope''' (''plural'' '''antelope''' or '''antelpopes''')

#Any of several African [[mammal]]s of the family ''[[Bovidae]]'' distinguished by having hollow [[horn]]s. Unlike [[deer]] antelope do not shed their horns.

